# Phase 3 — Terraform infrastructure

Remote state: S3 + DynamoDB lock (to be created manually first, then referenced)

Planned modules:
- `modules/vpc/` — 2 AZ, public + private subnets
- `modules/eks/` — cluster + managed node group (2x t3.medium)
- `modules/ecr/` — `qr-api`, `qr-frontend` repos
- `modules/s3/` — QR code bucket (private, versioned, 30-day lifecycle)
- `modules/iam/` — IRSA roles for api, External Secrets, ArgoCD, cert-manager
- `modules/secrets-manager/` — runtime AWS keys for api pod

Cost discipline: `terraform destroy` whenever not actively demoing.
